### ========================================
### 4. ITEMS CRUD (Butuh Token)
### ========================================

### [1] Create Item Baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop ASUS ROG",
  "description": "Gaming laptop RTX 4060",
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 15000000,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

### [2] Get All Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [3] Get Items dengan Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [4] Get Items Filter Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items?category=Electronics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [5] Get Items Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items?search=laptop
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [6] Get Single Item by ID (Ganti 1 dengan ID item)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [7] Update Item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop ASUS ROG Strix",
  "quantity": 15,
  "price": 18000000
}

### [8] Delete Item (Ganti 1 dengan ID item)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [9] Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### 5. TEST ERROR HANDLING
### ========================================

### Tanpa Token (Harus 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items

### Token Invalid (Harus 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_12345

### Get Item Not Found (Harus 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Item Invalid (Negative Quantity)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Item",
  "quantity": -5,
  "price": 100000
}

### Route Not Found (Harus 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/route-not-exist